://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879480/extras/GIF-1.gif?t=1728474505\" /><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>VN Style story with dynamic camera angles, and outfits you select<br></li><li>An immersive storyline filled with emotional twists and moments that will make your heart race<br></li><li>Embark on a journey that will connect you with a world of your fantasies and the search for truth<br></li><li>Make crucial choices that will determine the fate of the character and his path to victory<br></li><li>Diverse characters, each with unique personality traits and backgrounds, making your journey even more intriguing</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"It's a start!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/9ffd33b17d99c56a08364b56cfb65ab55f936a32.jpg"},{"name":"You decided to help Mercy with her father.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/7fb154ea53cb36651d14709b9ee9391099161e9d.jpg"},{"name":"You decided to go to the interview.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/67bd9eeb2e4bfb9ba2501554adbdb010cf9b1d15.jpg"},{"name":"The boss's daughter is one hell of a girl.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/1ac8afe970be3b35dbf1e0992a43043289b99ece.jpg"},{"name":"Adrenaline rush.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/5a44bac6c4aa2f1d9f510fef5db7fbb761985ce2.jpg"},{"name":"A night of passion.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/5850aed529b5bedafd577417018e27eda92cf3fc.jpg"},{"name":"Let's reminisce.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2879480/b37c19aa433e45841d12da2a68f0c7a51f885be4.jpg"},{"name":"The hero of romance novels","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public